{#
  src/reporting/templates/removal_report.md.j2
  TraceBurn Removal Progress Report — Jinja2 Markdown template

  Required variables:
    profile_name   (str)  — Display name of the profile, e.g. "Jane Smith"
    generated_at   (str)  — Report generation timestamp, e.g. "2026-04-01 09:14:32 UTC"
    period_start   (str)  — Start of the reporting period, e.g. "2026-03-10"
    period_end     (str)  — End of the reporting period (typically today)
    removals       (list) — List of removal records, each:
                              broker_name      (str)
                              removal_tier     (int): 1 | 2 | 3
                              method           (str): "Playwright" | "Email" | "Manual"
                              status           (str): "confirmed" | "pending" | "failed" | "reappeared"
                              submitted_at     (str | None)
                              confirmed_at     (str | None)
                              days_to_confirm  (int | None)
                              failure_reason   (str | None)
                              retry_scheduled  (str | None)
                              next_verify_at   (str | None)
    summary        (dict) — {
                               total      (int),
                               submitted  (int),
                               confirmed  (int),
                               pending    (int),
                               failed     (int),
                               reappeared (int)
                             }
    proof_records  (list) — List of proof record entries, each:
                              broker_name      (str)
                              proof_type       (str): "Screenshot" | "HTTP 200" | "Manual"
                              captured_at      (str)
                              checksum_status  (str): "valid" | "invalid" | "missing"
    proof_count    (int)  — Total proof records on file
    checksum_ok    (int)  — Count of proofs with valid checksums
    avg_days_confirmed (float | None) — Average days to confirmation (confirmed removals only)

  Sample rendered output:
    # TraceBurn Removal Progress Report

    Generated: 2026-04-01 09:14:32 UTC
    Period:    2026-03-10 → 2026-04-01

    ## Summary Counts

    | Status                 | Count |
    |------------------------|-------|
    | Total Removals Tracked | 14    |
    ...
#}
# TraceBurn Removal Progress Report

**Generated:** {{ generated_at }}
**Period:** {{ period_start }} → {{ period_end }}
**Profile:** {{ profile_name }}

---

## Summary Counts

| Status | Count |
|--------|-------|
| Total Removals Tracked | {{ summary.total }} |
| Submitted | {{ summary.submitted }} |
| Confirmed Removed | {{ summary.confirmed }} |
| Pending Verification | {{ summary.pending }} |
| Failed / Retry Needed | {{ summary.failed }} |
| Reappeared | {{ summary.reappeared }} |

**Proof Records on File:** {{ proof_count }} records
**Checksum Integrity:** {% if proof_count > 0 %}{% if checksum_ok == proof_count %}All valid ({{ checksum_ok }}/{{ proof_count }}){% else %}⚠️ {{ proof_count - checksum_ok }} invalid ({{ checksum_ok }}/{{ proof_count }} valid){% endif %}{% else %}N/A — no proof records yet{% endif %}

{% if avg_days_confirmed is not none %}
**Average days to confirmation** (confirmed only): {{ "%.1f" | format(avg_days_confirmed) }} days
{% endif %}

